<div class="investment_summary">
  <h3>Investment Summary</h3>

  <h4>Initial Rate of Return</h4>
  <p>Based on a current price of $<%= dollar_value(@report[:report_summary][:initial_rate_of_return][:current_price]) %></p>
  <p>Estimated Earnings: <%= dollar_value(@report[:report_summary][:initial_rate_of_return][:estimated_earnings]) %></p>
  <p>Initial Rate of Return: <%= @report[:report_summary][:initial_rate_of_return][:initial_rate_of_return] %>%</p>
  <p>Value Relative to Government Bonds: <%= @report[:report_summary][:initial_rate_of_return][:value_relative_to_government_bonds] %></p>

  <h4>Dividends versus Retained Earnings</h4>
  <p>Dividends: <%= @report[:report_summary][:dividend_percentage] %>%</p>
  <p>Retained Earnings: <%= @report[:report_summary][:retained_earnings_percentage] %>%</p>

  <h4>PE Ratio</h4>
  <p>Range: <%= @report[:report_summary][:pe_ratio][:lowest_pe_ratio] %> - <%= @report[:report_summary][:pe_ratio][:highest_pe_ratio] %></p>
  <p>Average high: <%= @report[:report_summary][:pe_ratio][:average_high_pe_ratio] %></p>
  <p>Average low: <%= @report[:report_summary][:pe_ratio][:average_low_pe_ratio] %></p>

  <h4>Growth</h4>
  <p>Per Share Growth Rate: <%= @report[:report_summary][:growth][:per_share_growth_rate] %>%</p>
</div>
